        {
            "title": "中東最大鋁生產商阿聯酋環球鋁業的冶煉廠停運 伊朗襲擊嚴重破壞運營",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據一位知情人士透露，中東最大鋁生產商阿聯酋環球鋁業在其塔維拉(Al Taweelah)冶煉廠於周末遭伊朗飛彈和無人機襲擊後，已停止該設施的運營。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位因信息未公開而要求匿名的人士表示，位於阿布達比郊外的這座冶煉廠因襲擊而斷電，其電解生產線被迫發生失控停機。知情人士稱，金屬已在冶煉回路內凝固，對運營造成重大破壞。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">倫敦金屬交易所鋁期貨自襲擊發生以來大幅上漲。海灣地區另一家主要生產商巴林鋁業也證實，其運營設施在周末遭到伊朗襲擊。這兩座工廠的規模居全球前列，2025年鋁產量各達到160萬噸。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-789a0116-6c88-3af0-933d-2ccd5ea56178-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：中東鋁生產商遭伊朗襲擊 加劇供應危機風險 (3)</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">整個中東地區約占全球鋁供應的9%，阿聯酋環球鋁業等企業在向歐洲、亞洲和美國製造商供貨方面發揮關鍵作用。甚至在該行業直接成為襲擊目標之前，霍爾木茲海峽實際上的封鎖就已使該地區主要生產商缺少關鍵投入品。業內預計，若海峽不能盡快重開，將出現減產連鎖反應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Top Gulf Aluminum Producer EGA Halted Smelter After Iran Strike</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
