        {
            "title": "美國製造業擴張速度創2022年來最高 伊朗戰爭推動投入成本躍升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Institute for Supply Management\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"811\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nF8ZNOZ3lOEJ2uWUt8I75w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgxMQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1847ead819dd8628ae96f665da2b39aa\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Institute for Supply Management</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國3月份<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"製造業\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:製造業;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/製造業\">製造業</a>活動擴張速度創2022年以來最高，而受伊朗戰爭影響，投入價格繼續飆升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">供應管理學會(ISM)製造業支付價格指數攀升7.8點至78.3，維持在2022年年中以來的最高水平。過去兩個月，該指數合計上漲了19.3點，創近十年來最大漲幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">受伊朗戰爭影響，霍爾木茲海峽接近關閉，阻礙了石油和其他製造業關鍵產品的運輸。這導致油價飆升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管如此，ISM製造業指數小幅上升至52.7，生產成長走強和供應商交付指標上升形成提振。支付價格上漲和交貨周期延長可能反映了衝突導致貿易擾動的影響。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c886b4c6-2dfa-390c-97f7-236bfe3d25b8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"811\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IS7FSnJ_s_ZdXfkFp9o2Vg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgxMQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/bd2981bb146db5fdff819dd9f8f24f73\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「3月總體評論中有64%是負面的。」ISM製造業企業調查委員會主席Susan Spence在一份聲明中表示，「在負面評論中，約20%提到了關稅，約40%提到了中東戰爭。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上月共有13個製造業行業報告成長，其中包括初級金屬和運輸設備行業。另有3個行業出現收縮。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">供應商交付指標升至2022年5月以來最高。除了能源之外，霍爾木茲海峽還是鋁、化肥，甚至是用於半導體生產的氦氣等產品的咽喉要道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投入成本上升可能會迫使美國製造商提高價格，這意味著全年整體通膨率將走高。彭博最近的一項調查顯示，經濟學家上調了對通膨的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ISM報告還顯示，3月新訂單和積壓訂單成長穩健，但增速放緩。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，ISM製造業就業指標變化不大。儘管該指數仍接近一年多來的最高水平，但這一指標表明，3月製造業員工人數持續收縮。美國勞工統計局將於周五發布3月就業報告。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Manufacturing Expands Most Since 2022, Input Costs Jump (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%A5%AD%E6%93%B4%E5%BC%B5%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E5%89%B52022%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E6%8A%95%E5%85%A5%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E8%BA%8D%E5%8D%87-145100572.html",
